Hisse Ekle
</button>

<div class="hp-err" id="hpErr"><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none"><circle cx="7.5" cy="7.5" r="6.5" stroke="#b91c1c" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M7.5 4v4M7.5 10.5v.5" stroke="#b91c1c" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg><span id="hpErrMsg"></span></div>
<div class="hp-warn" id="hpWarn"><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 15 15" fill="none"><path d="M7.5 2L14 13H1L7.5 2Z" stroke="#d97706" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M7.5 6v3M7.5 10.5v.5" stroke="#d97706" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg><span id="hpWarnMsg"></span></div>

<div class="hp-btns">
<button class="hp-calc" id="hpCalcBtn" type="button">
<svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><rect x="2" y="2" width="5" height="5" rx="1" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/><rect x="9" y="2" width="5" height="5" rx="1" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/><rect x="2" y="9" width="5" height="5" rx="1" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M9 11.5h5M11.5 9v5" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
Hesapla
</button>
<button class="hp-clear" id="hpClearBtn" type="button">Temizle</button>
</div>

<div class="hp-info"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><circle cx="7" cy="7" r="6" stroke="#C8A24A" stroke-width="1.2"/><path d="M7 6v4M7 4.5v.5" stroke="#C8A24A" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg> Girilen hisse oranlarının en küçük ortak paydası (EKOK) hesaplanarak tüm hisseler aynı payda üzerinden yeniden ifade edilir.</div>
</div>

<div class="hp-card">
<div class="hp-empty" id="hpEmpty">
<div class="hp-empty-icon"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none"><path d="M6 5H9M6 9H9M6 13H9M13 5H16M13 9H16M13 13H16" stroke="#7a90a8" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/><rect x="3" y="3" width="8" height="16" rx="1.5" stroke="#7a90a8" stroke-width="1.5"/><rect x="11" y="3" width="8" height="16" rx="1.5" stroke="#7a90a8" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg></div>
<p>Hisseleri girin ve Hesapla butonuna basın.</p>
</div>
<div class="hp-res" id="hpRes"></div>
</div>

</div>

<div class="hp-disc">
<div class="hp-disc-head"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="6.5" stroke="#7a90a8" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M8 7v5M8 5v.5" stroke="#7a90a8" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg><span>Bilgilendirme Notu</span></div>
<p>Bu araç, farklı paydalara sahip hisse oranlarını ortak paydaya dönüştürmek için hazırlanmıştır. Kat irtifakı, kat mülkiyeti ve benzeri işlemlerde teknik kontrol amacıyla kullanılabilir. Resmi işlem ve tescil süreçlerinde ilgili Tapu Müdürlüğü ve yetkili uzmanların değerlendirmesi esas alınmalıdır.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<style>
.fab-wrap{position:fixed;bottom:24px;right:24px;z-index:9999;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end;gap:10px}
.fab-items{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end;gap:8px;pointer-events:none;opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px);transition:opacity .2s ease,transform .2s ease}
.fab-items.open{pointer-events:auto;opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}
.fab-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;text-decoration:none}
.fab-lbl{background:rgba(20,40,64,.92);color:#fff;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;padding:6px 12px;border-radius:8px;white-space:nowrap;letter-spacing:.01em;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(15,28,46,.25)}
.fab-dot{width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:var(--surface,#fff);border:2px solid var(--border,#dde3ec);box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(15,28,46,.12);transition:background .15s,border-color .15s,color .15s;flex-shrink:0;color:#3d5068}
.fab-item:hover .fab-dot{background:#2a4f7c;border-color:#2a4f7c;color:#fff}
.fab-item.fab-active .fab-dot{background:#C8A24A;border-color:#C8A24A;color:#142840;box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(200,162,74,.4)}
.fab-item.fab-active .fab-lbl{background:rgba(200,162,74,.12);color:#debb6e;border:1px solid rgba(200,162,74,.3)}
.fab-item.fab-active{pointer-events:none;cursor:default}
.fab-toggle{width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:50%;background:#1E3A5F;border:none;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(15,28,46,.35);transition:transform .2s ease,background .2s ease;flex-shrink:0}
.fab-toggle:hover{background:#2a4f7c;transform:scale(1.06)}.fab-toggle:active{transform:scale(.96)}
.fab-toggle.open{background:#142840}
.fab-ti{transition:transform .25s ease;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.fab-toggle.open .fab-ti{transform:rotate(45deg)}
@media(max-width:480px){.fab-wrap{bottom:16px;right:16px}.fab-lbl{font-size:11px;padding:5px 10px}}
@media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.fab-items,.fab-toggle,.fab-ti{transition:none}}
</style>

